<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title%></title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header class="header">
        <nav>
          <ul class="menu-items" id="tabs">
            <li class="menu-btn hov-style" data-name="index">
              <a aria-label="Home Page" href="../dist/index.html">Home</a>
            </li>

            <div
              class="dropdown-div menu-btn gal-hov dropdown-btn"
              data-name="galleries"
              title="Galleries"
            >
              <div class="gal-btn-div">
                <li aria-label="Click to Open Submenu">
                  <a href="#galleries">Galleries</a>
                </li>

                <div class="gal-arrow"></div>
              </div>

              <ul class="dropdown-content">
                <li
                  class="dropdown-item birds"
                  style="--delay: 1"
                  data-name="birds-gallery"
                  aria-label="Click to Visit Gallery"
                >
                  <a href="../dist/birds-gallery.html">Birds</a>
                </li>
                <li
                  class="dropdown-item insects"
                  style="--delay: 2"
                  data-name="insects-gallery"
                  aria-label="Click to Visit Gallery"
                >
                  <a href="../dist/insects-gallery.html">Insects</a>
                </li>
                <li
                  class="dropdown-item small-animals"
                  style="--delay: 3"
                  data-name="small-animals-gallery"
                  aria-label="Click to Visit Gallery"
                >
                  <a href="../dist/small-animals-gallery.html">Small Animals</a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <li class="menu-btn hov-style" data-name="about">
              <a
                aria-label="About Page"
                aria-current="page"
                href="../dist/about.html"
                >About</a
              >
            </li>

            <li class="menu-btn hov-style" data-name="contact">
              <a aria-label="Contact Page" href="../dist/contact.html"
                >Contact</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <main class="main">
        <!-- ABOUT -->
        <section class="tab-content" id="about">
          <div class="about">
            <div class="about-text-div">
              <div class="bosco-entry">
                <p class="definition" aria-label="dictionary entry">
                  <strong>bosco</strong> - noun [masculine] - wood, forest
                </p>
                <p
                  class="definition"
                  aria-label="dictionary example phrase, Italian to English translation"
                >
                  <em>gli animali del bosco:</em> forest animals
                </p>
                <p class="definition" aria-label="dictionary entry attribution">
                  dictionary.cambridge.org - Italian to English Dictionary, June
                  2024
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="about-box" aria-label="about text: 2 paragraphs">
                <p class="about-text">
                  Hi! I'm Jenn Guneratne, the New England-based photographer
                  behind Bosco Images Wildlife Photography. I studied digital
                  photography in the early 2010s, but I didn't fall into
                  wildlife photography until much later. The journey began at
                  the edge of the woods in my local area, capturing small
                  animals, birds and insects.
                </p>
                <p class="about-text last-para">
                  I spend a lot of spare time during the warmer months outside,
                  either working on my garden, or walking with my cat on his
                  harness around the house. This allows for a lot of time to
                  observe the wildlife that lives nearby, and a few of my
                  current favorite shots can be attributed to my cat lazing in
                  one place, allowing me time to quietly capture the nearby
                  wildlife. These galleries mark the beginning of much more to
                  come as I expand further afield (albeit without my cat in
                  toe).
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="footer-div">
        <div class="footer">
          <div class="copyright-div">
            <p class="my-copyright">Jenn Guneratne Â© 2024</p>
          </div>

          <div class="logo-div">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/jguneratne/photo-gallery"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              <img
                src="<%=require('../src/assets/imgs/github-mark.svg') %>"
                alt="Octocat GitHub Logo"
                class="github-logo"
              />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
